# Add item to "Create New" Menu
1. Create ~/.kde4/share/templates if it doesn't exsit.
2. Add a desktop file in it with URL entry pointing to template file.
   Example:

    ~~~ 
[Desktop Entry]
Comment=New Texmacs Document
Encoding=UTF-8
Name=Texmacs Document
Type=Link
URL=$HOME/Templates/template.tm
    ~~~

3. Create template at the path pointed by URL

